    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc.
                            3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [49] Seu et <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3431"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ecclesia</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3442">Sancti Laurenti</placeName></orgName> quam
                            <name ref="Airaldus">Ayroaldou</name>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachou</rs> edificavit loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/3442">Treventus</placeName>, ubi et se et
                        uxorem suam nomine <name ref="Bessoara">Bessoara</name> et filium suum
                        nomine <name ref="Stephanus">Stephanum</name> monastice tradidit
                        conversationi, postea vero et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et omnes
                        facultates suas et se ipsum et uxorem suam et filium suum <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/85" key="#Monasteries"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/110">Sancte Sophie</placeName></orgName>
                        optulit, nostra vero eximietas omnia et in omnibus mobilia et inmobilia
                        secundum <rs key="#Cartula #Offersio/donatio">textum offertionis</rs>
                        predicto Sancte Sophie monasterio firmabimus possidendum. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
